props.synopsis: A man has been arrested in the US state of Arizona in connection with the shooting of two young police officers and a civilian neighbour in the rural Queensland community of Wieambilla last year.

image.altText: Woman wearing a white top with bright pink hair.

image.altText: Hats and other objects left in a sandy field

This is what we know about the investigation. WARNING: Readers may find some of the details in this story distressing.

title.children: Israel has levelled shocking allegations of sexual violence against Hamas. Here's what we know

image.altText: An ambulance speeds down a road.

title.children: Third Queenslander in a month dies waiting for medical help

image.altText: Close up of Bruce Lerhmann.

title.children: Bruce Lehrmann and Brittany Higgins getting 'quite touchy' in club on night of alleged rape, witness tells court

title.children: 'We cannot let him win': Biden says he is not sure he'd be running if Trump wasn't in the race

image.altText: A man in a blue shirt is surrounded by reporters with microphones and cameras.

image.altText: An older man in a blazer wears a municipal medallion and stands in front of a historic-looking building.

image.altText: People wearing white aprons sit around a table and eat food. They have large platters in front of them and all look happy.
